{"title":"中国画","authors":["孙友田"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙友田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天翻地覆之后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月的妙手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将大地失落的热量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"研磨成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流动的黑色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼在一页页岩石上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深的地层下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现了一幅又一幅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有黑色的山峦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的丛林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的河流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的湖泊……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机将地下的画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬挂在油田上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桔红色的头盔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀在井架旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是每幅画都有了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初升的太阳。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}